SEO AUDIT REPORT
usfinnexus.com
Prepared: March 2026  |  Full Site Evaluation

Overall SEO Score: 54/100 — Significant improvement opportunities identified

1. Executive Summary
USFinNexus.com is a newly launched (February 2026) free mortgage and personal finance calculator platform targeting US consumers. The site has a clear value proposition — spam-free, no lender referrals, professional-grade tools — and competes directly against high-authority domains including Bankrate, NerdWallet, Zillow, and Calculator.net.

The site has solid foundational structure but has critical gaps in technical SEO, on-page optimization, E-E-A-T signals, link authority, and content depth. Without addressing these, ranking for competitive finance keywords will be extremely difficult regardless of content quality.

2. SEO Scorecard
Category	Score	Summary
